00:29:16,446 --> 00:29:18,989
Dan terima kasih.

342
00:29:18,990 --> 00:29:21,808
Sungguh. / Bagus.

343
00:29:25,288 --> 00:29:27,189
Selamat tinggal.

344
00:29:31,836 --> 00:29:33,737
Yah...

345
00:29:33,963 --> 00:29:36,073
